milestones.description: Kevin O'Brien has become the top wicket-taker for IRE in ODIs with 68 wickets, going past Johnston's 66
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Shapoor's 3
Craig Young has taken the most five-wicket hauls (1) in ODIs for IRE, going past vd Merwe's record
Samiullah Shinwari has scored 8 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record

stories.title: Zadran onslaught too much for Ireland
stories.subTitle: Afghanistan v Ireland, Dubai Triangular Series
stories.seoTitle: Najibullah Zadran onslaught too much for Ireland
stories.summary: Afghanistan responded to their heavy defeat against Scotland by inflicting a 71-run loss on Ireland which means the final match on Monday will decide who comes out on top
